The '''Independent Ship Owners''' or '''ISO''' was an independent shipping guild that operated out of [[Coruscant/Legends|Coruscant]] during the [[Galactic Civil War/Legends|Galactic Civil War]]. The ''[[Tuk Prevoz]]'' was one of its ships.

